profile:
WELCOME TO CC MINI BIN RENTALS - WORKING HOURS,7 Days a Week: 24Hrs! 
SOCIAL MEDIA: Facebook,Instagram,Google

The company was established in 2017 and in a short period of time has built a strong reputation for their quality of service in both the residential and corporate sectors. 
CC Mini Bin Rentals is a new and innovative waste management company that provides disposable waste bin rentals with speedy and exceptional customer service. The company is certified with The WSIB (Workplace Safety & Insurance Board) and is a fully insured organization. Let the team at CC Mini Bin Rentals handle your next waste management project!
Our team is dedicated to what we do and we would love to assist you with your disposal needs. Here at CC Mini Bin Rentals we offer a variety of disposal bins sizes to choose from which include the following sizes:

4 Yard Bin: LENGTH: 12 Feet (144 Inches),WIDTH: 5 Feet (60 Inches),HEIGHT: 2 Feet (24 Inches), WASTE TYPE: Mixed Garbage, Soil, Concrete, Bricks, Blocks and Asphalt

12 Yard Bin: LENGTH: 12 Feet (144 Inches),WIDTH: 5 Feet (60 Inches),HEIGHT: 5.5 Feet (66 Inches)
 WASTE TYPE: Mixed Garbage

16 Yard Bin: LENGTH: 12 Feet (144 Inches),WIDTH: 6 Feet (72 Inches),HEIGHT: 6 Feet (72 Inches)
 WASTE TYPE: Mixed Garbage

20 Yard Bin: LENGTH: 13 Feet (156 Inches),WIDTH: 7 Feet (84 Inches),HEIGHT: 6 Feet (72 Inches) 
WASTE TYPE: Mixed Garbage

In addition we provide 
Crane service
Landscape Material
Float Service 

CC Min Bin Rentals is a family run business that services the Greater Toronto Area including Vaughan, Richmond Hill, Thornhill, Brampton, Bradford, Innisfill, Barrie, King City, Orangeville, New Tecumseth and Alliston.
